strings: <voice_0x0100184E><se_low>Jungmi: I hope it has been a long time since we have met in human form like this.
<voice_0x0100184F><se_low>*: Delivery in May! ...... Everything's all right? possibly not!
<voice_0x01001850><se_low>Jungmi: This is not a problem. Now he knows everything. He lives in a retirement home in Dragovia.
<voice_0x01001851><se_low>*: Ah, I'm relieved... Then why are you hanging around like me?
<voice_0x01001852><se_low>Jungmi: This is me. Why pick the one I love? everything is good. You're ready!
<voice_0x01001853><se_low>*: ... it's handy because I have a bag with me. It should not be mounted?
<voice_0x01001854><se_low>Jungmi: I follow! I am back in human form to be satisfied!
<voice_0x01001855><se_low>Jungmi: Thank you very much for your hard work. My gratitude is wide like the ocean.
<voice_0x01001856><se_low>Jungmi: ...well... it's time to go back to your body, I'm sorry.
